            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Not a dashboard tool — output, not diagnostics</li>
                <li>Built for cadence, not one-off articles</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Operators who want SEO output every month without learning a tool stack.</div>
            <a href="/checkout/" class="tool-cta-btn">Start at $99/mo →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">02</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Search Atlas (OTTO SEO)</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best technical + on-page autopilot</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$149<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Starter plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
