              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Content generation is bolt-on, not the core strength</li>
                <li>OTTO script needs CMS access — extra setup</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Sites with 500+ pages needing autonomous on-page fixes at scale.</div>
            <a href="https://searchatlas.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
