            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>You still write and publish manually</li>
                <li>No technical or off-page automation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Content teams that already have writers and want SERP-aware scoring.</div>
            <a href="https://surferseo.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
